input_args.text: "Muslims in Kashmir observe martyrdom anniv. of 4th Shia Imam Thu Oct 27, 2016 10:7PM Shia Muslims in Kashmir mark the martyrdom anniversary of 4th Shia Imam Zainul Abideen. © Press TV \nSyed Ali SafviPress TV, Indian-controlled Kashmir \nMourning processions have been held across Indian-controlled Kashmir to mark the martyrdom anniversary of 4th Shia Imam Zainul Abideen. As Press TV's Syed Ali Safvi says, black-clad mourners have marched through the streets of Kashmir, beating their chests and reciting soul-stirring eulogies. Loading ..."
